{html}<div><p>I vote +1 for fixing this!<br>
Another example, KS -&gt; Controls -&gt; "Butto" with "n"
wrapped</p></div>{html}

{html}<div><p>I think this is to do with auto-detecting the width. As a
workaround, you can explicitly set a large enough width and the
text won't wrap. Obviously, this is not ideal, though.</p></div>{html}

{html}<div><p>Thanks for the note, Don.<br>
Another workaround is to change the fontsize. Increasing/decreasing
by just one point can correct the problem</p></div>{html}
